  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下nilearn文档部署的完整流程。核心问题是：PR构建的文档怎么预览，以及正式发布怎么走到nilearn.github.io的dev和stable分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DocumentationBuilder",
        "nilearn_doc_dev",
        "nilearn_doc_stable",
        "trigger_hosting"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我理解为有三个主要部分：Circle-CI侧、目标部署仓库nilearn.github.io、以及源码仓库nilearn本身。在nilearn仓库里，build-docs.yml是主要的构建工作流对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Circle-CI",
        "GitHub - nilearn.github.io",
        "GitHub - nilearn",
        "DocumentationBuilder"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，build-docs.yml就是DocumentationBuilder。它有三条触发路径：main分支提交、GitHub release发布、以及PR提交。前两个直接部署到nilearn.github.io，但PR的处理方式不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DocumentationBuilder",
        "main",
        "GitHub release",
        "PR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我这样画：DocumentationBuilder在main分支上指向nilearn_doc_dev，release时指向nilearn_doc_stable。PR场景下它同时产出artifacts和触发trigger_hosting_on_pr.yml。这样区分对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DocumentationBuilder",
        "nilearn_doc_dev",
        "nilearn_doc_stable",
        "artifacts",
        "trigger_hosting"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "方向是对的，但注意artifacts是文档构建产物，不是直接部署，而是用docs形状表示。trigger_hosting_on_pr.yml会触发Circle-CI里的host_docs job来做实际托管。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "artifacts",
        "trigger_hosting",
        "nilearn_CCI",
        "host docs job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我调整了。现在artifacts用docs形状，并且用虚线标注\"fetched by\"指向Circle-CI的host_docs job。trigger_hosting用实线\"triggers\"连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "artifacts",
        "nilearn_CCI",
        "trigger_hosting"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，nilearn_doc_dev和nilearn_doc_stable的label需要准确。它们对应的是<code/dev和<code/stable目录，不是分支名。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "nilearn_doc_dev",
        "nilearn_doc_stable"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，已修正。nilearn_doc_dev标注为\"<code/dev\"，nilearn_doc_stable标注为\"<code/stable\"。另外确认一下：DocumentationBuilder到这两个节点的关系，main和release的标注方式需要区分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "nilearn_doc_dev",
        "nilearn_doc_stable",
        "DocumentationBuilder",
        "main",
        "GitHub release"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
