    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。现在三条线都带上了条件标注。PR那条线我画成分叉，同时指向artifacts和trigger_hosting，表示并行产出。",
      "elements_involved": [
