    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "最后确认Circle-CI部分的命名。子图叫\"Circle-CI\"，里面的节点是host_docs job，但图里我们用nilearn_CCI作为节点ID来引用。",
      "elements_involved": [
